data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER...LOOK NO FURTHER; A MUST SEE!!! Discover the essence of hidden charm with this breathtaking home in the desirable community of Berkeley Manor that promises an exquisite living experience. Nestled in a serene location, this spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom 1,750 sq. split-plan property offers the allure of a true hidden gem. It features a beautifully manicured front and back yard with fantastic curb appeal. The entrance to this home is reminiscent of walking into a Spanish villa with its many arched doorways, beamed ceilings, and designer touches throughout the house. The house features crown molding, bathroom upgrades, gutter guards, granite counters, hardwood flooring, plantation shutters, state of the art washer/dryer, kitchen appliances for perfect decor, and even a custom-built office in the garage for a true man-cave experience. It offers ample room for comfort living with a spacious floor plan and is perfect for those who value the privacy of owners and guests alike in your very own e-suite master bedroom with double sinks and a spacious walk-in closet. A formal living room and dining room is perfect for entertaining guests and is fully accessible through the lanai. Not ready to entertain? Step into your separate family room and eating area for an intimate and cozy experience. The comforts of this property are many such as central air and heating throughout the house. Yes, even in the office located in the garage. The property is conveniently situated in a tranquil cul-de-sac surrounded by nearby shopping and eateries such as Target, Publix, and one of the best pizza spots in town, Rocco’s Pizza. A pet friendly community with tranquil surroundings conveniently located in the Hernando School District with three major schools in close proximity. For outdoor enthusiasts and park lovers alike check out Weeki Wachee Springs, State Park, Linda Pederson Park, and Buccaneer Bay Waterpark just a few minutes away. Looking for the biggest, best tasting avocado in town? Look no further. This property has the best grown avocados found in all of Spring Hill. And it can all be yours now. So if you’re looking for that WOW factor, look no more! Call to schedule your showing today and walk out with the home of your dreams. House is currently VACANT, pics were taken before Estate Sale.
